               "# Miniforge.ai Header & Copyright\n\n<version>1.0.0</version>\n\n## Context\n- Use when authoring or editing site, docs, blog, or README content.\n\n## Requirements\n- Include this header block verbatim at the top of content.\n- Use copyright owner: Christopher Lester (christopher@miniforge.ai).\n- Do not attribute copyright to Miniforge.ai as an entity. ✅\n\n## Examples\n<example>\n  Title: Miniforge.ai\n  Subtitle: An agentic SDLC / fleet-control platform\n  Author: Christopher Lester\n  Line: Founder, Miniforge.ai (project)\n  Copyright 2025-2026 Christopher Lester (christopher@miniforge.ai)\n</example>\n\n<example type=\"invalid\">\n  Copyright 2025 miniforge.ai\n</example>",
